01:13:09,632 --> 01:13:11,827
and during the week
will begin testing the car.

378
01:13:17,808 --> 01:13:19,900
VOICE OF ALAIN PROST

379
01:14:00,549 --> 01:14:03,143
I'm pretty sure of one thing:

380
01:14:03,953 --> 01:14:08,117
I'm the one that has more to lose.

381
01:14:08,257 --> 01:14:11,249
if I had to stop for a year or more,

382
01:14:11,360 --> 01:14:15,262
Because I'm at an age near the peak of my career

489
01:14:15,331 --> 01:14:20,234
and the number of years in the career
of a Formula One driver is limited.

383
01:14:23,105 --> 01:14:27,838
So if I stop, I'd lose out
more than anyone else,

384
01:14:27,943 --> 01:14:31,242
both professionally and personally.

385
01:14:32,948 --> 01:14:37,009
ADRIANE GALISTEU

386
01:14:47,229 --> 01:14:51,598
In 1993, Ayrton drove
his car so brilliantly.

387
01:14:51,734 --> 01:14:53,599
For me, it was his best season.

