416
01:22:01,863 --> 01:22:03,296
REGINALDO LEME
GLOBO TV COMMENTATOR

417
01:22:08,003 --> 01:22:11,495
I never saw him smile,
even for a moment.

418
01:22:12,975 --> 01:22:17,036
He maintained a bemused, bored, even a sad demeanour.

