01:28:55,644 --> 01:28:59,136
SUNDAY
1st MAY 1994

440
01:29:36,718 --> 01:29:39,084
That morning when I awoke,

441
01:29:39,154 --> 01:29:40,416
VIVIANE SENNA
AYRTON'S SISTER

442
01:29:40,488 --> 01:29:42,285
God asked me to speak to him.

443
01:29:43,758 --> 01:29:47,885
He opened the Bible and
read a passage that said

444
01:29:47,962 --> 01:29:52,990
God would give him
the greatest gift of all,

445
01:29:54,402 --> 01:29:57,803
that of God himself.

